snippet.title: "Voyage - A Sorceress' Vacation" for Sega Master System (Version 1.0 Launch Trailer, New Homebrew)
snippet.description:
Help our heroine to start her much needed vacation and check out what this strange island that you stranded on is all about by grabbing the IPS patch and infos on how to patch here: https://www.smspower.org/Hacks/AlexKiddInMiracleWorld-SMS-VoyageASorceressVacation-Mod

The full ROM can be downloaded here: https://archive.org/details/voyageasorceressvacation1.0segamastersystem

The game formerly known as "Ma Kai Quest" started development in 2016 and is now ready to download for everybody to play on your favourite Master System emulator (that you can download here: https://emulicious.net/) or flashcarts for your Master System, Mega Drive or Game Gear.

Release Page on ROMhacking.net: https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/4873/
Soundtrack: http://mandulin.de/voyage-soundtrack.html
